metadata.name: The Fire Inside
metadata.description:
sometimes it burns bright  
other times it is like a dying star  
in the last night sky  
maybe it is the soul wanting to speak?

the flame that flickers like an untamed dance  
the flame that dims like a failing streetlamp  
but even the littlest of all fires  
can light a beacon  
or guide a lost ship in a silent sea

so come and sit here by the fire inside  
and let it kindle  
by letting it be
